node.text: Your kitchen and dining room are the core gathering spots for fall celebrations, so welcome guests with warm autumn accents that are chic, functional, and easily tailored to your event and style. For more home decor inspiration, follow us on social media.

node.text: Embrace the coziest season of the year with simple tips to add an autumn touch to your mantel and living room—no major changes required. Like this video and follow our channel for more decor inspiration.

node.text: Whether you’re decorating by the front door or all around the porch, the tips in this video will help you make a stunning first-impression, just in time for fall. So let’s dial up the curb appeal and enter the harvest season in style. And for more inspiration, follow our channel.

node.text: Create an elevated farmhouse vibe with a simple DIY! Staple chicken wire to an open frame and decorate with your favorite accent pieces to recreate a similar look.
